    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;YANG (RFC 7950) is a data modeling language used to model configuration data, state data, parameters and results of Remote Procedure Call (RPC) operations or actions, and notifications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document defines encoding rules for YANG in the Concise Binary Object Representation (CBOR) (RFC 8949).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
